    def tsne_visualization(emb, stim_ids, fs_label=14, fn_legend=14, show_legend=False, title=""):
    fig, axs = plt.subplots(figsize=(5,5), facecolor='w')
    unique_stim_ids = np.unique(stim_ids)
    for stim_id in unique_stim_ids:
        mask = (stim_ids==stim_id)
        axs.scatter(emb[mask,0], emb[mask,1], label=stim_id)
    if show_legend:
        axs.legend(frameon=False, fontsize=fn_legend)
    if title!="":
        axs.set_title(title, fontsize=fs_label)
    axs.set_xlabel("1st component", fontsize=fs_label)
    axs.set_ylabel("2nd component", fontsize=fs_label)
    def tsne_visualization(emb, stim_ids, fs_label=14, fn_legend=14, show_legend=False, title=""): fig, axs = plt.subplots(figsize=(5,5), facecolor='w') unique_stim_ids = np.unique(stim_ids) for stim_id in unique_stim_ids: mask = (stim_ids==stim_id) axs.scatter(emb[mask,0], emb[mask,1], label=stim_id) if show_legend: axs.legend(frameon=False, fontsize=fn_legend) if title!="": axs.set_title(title, fontsize=fs_label) axs.set_xlabel("1st component", fontsize=fs_label) axs.set_ylabel("2nd component", fontsize=fs_label)
